ğŸ‘¥ Two Saints in One Shrine

Primary Samadhi: Dadaji Dhuniwale (Swami Keshvanandji) took his samadhi in November 1930  .

His chief disciple: Swami Hariharanandji (originally Bhanwarlal from Rajasthan) became known as Chhota Dadaji. He took samadhi nearby in 1941â€“42  .

